=======

Du skal aere din hustru

Before he turned to the story of Joan of Arc, the Danish cinema genius Carl
Theodor Dreyer fashioned this ahead-of-its-time examination of domestic life.
A deft comedy of gentle revenge, it is the story of a housewife who, with the
help of a wily nanny, turns the tables on her tyrannical husband. In it, Dreyer
combines lightness and humor with his customary meticulous craft and sense of
integrity. Master of the House, an enormous box-office success in its day, is a
jewel of the silent cinema.

